</text_item>
<text_item id="pb" component_id="pb_05" visible="false">
<value>Encryption plays an important role in guaranteeing data integrity. It involves using mathematical algorithms to break up data to make it unreadable to anyone who doesn't have the correct cryptographic key or password. The key or password is used to decrypt the data and return it to its original state.</value>
